body:
Rating a show:Killing eve

Without nameing anyone like i think i can do that. The show has this old 1900’s feel to it like the cold war just ended and everyone knows it. But its a weird thing. But that is not the case. Its modernly set cell phones high end cloths and murder. Yes hifg end murdsr is a thing. Lovely humans to act out roles that give the characters more depth then you cpuld ever ask for. It pulls you into the life of one of the main actors and then jerks tou around a lot of murder and tip toeing around talking about sex. Thats the funny bit. All the murder by someone so small like damn you gotta be careful who you meet in a bathroom.

10 put of 10

Sorry baby
